{{WP|Matt Damon}}, {{WP|Luke Hemsworth}}, and {{WP|Sam Neill}} reprised their roles as Actor [[Loki Laufeyson (Earth-199999)|Loki]], Actor Thor, and Actor [[Odin Borson (Earth-199999)|Odin]], respectively, from {{sl|Thor: Ragnarok}}.{{cite|ref=true|url= https://deadline.com/2021/01/matt-damon-thor-love-thunder-australia-covid-chris-hemsworth-1234675631/|title= Matt Damon Touches Down In Australia Ahead Of ‘Thor: Love And Thunder’ Role|work= Deadline|last= Wiseman|first= Andreas|date= January 18, 2021|accessdate= January 27, 2021}}{{cite|ref=true|url=https://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-9315633/Matt-Damon-joins-Luke-Hemsworth-Sam-Neill-set-Thor-Love-Thunder-Sydney.html|title= Matt Damon dons a flowing black wig as he joins Luke Hemsworth and Sam Neill on elaborate theatre-style set for Thor: Love and Thunder in Sydney|work= Daily Mail Online|last= Marta|first= Jary|date= March 02, 2021|accessdate= March 02, 2021}} {{WP|Melissa McCarthy}} joined them as a stage actress portraying [[Hela Odinsdottir (Earth-199999)|Hela]]. McCarthy's husband {{WP|Ben Falcone}} also appeared as the play's director.{{cite|ref=true|url= https://www.instagram.com/tv/CJNsYH4ASn_/?utm_source=ig_web_copy_link|title= Merry Christmas! (And we’ve prepared a monologue) @chrishemsworth @marvel @taikawaititi|work= Instagram|last= McCarthy|first= Melissa|date= December 25, 2020|accessdate= March 02, 2021}}{{cite|ref=true |url= https://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-9315905/Melissa-McCarthy-husband-Ben-Falcone-spotted-filming-scenes-Thor-Love-Thunder.html|title= EXCLUSIVE: Melissa McCarthy sports a huge green headpiece as she transforms into Hela with Luke Hemsworth and husband Ben Falcone as they begin filming Thor: Love And Thunder in Sydney after superfan couple said they were 'desperate' for roles|work= Deadline|last= Stamell|first= Demeter|date= March 02, 2021|accessdate= March 02, 2021}} {{WP|Sean Gunn}} reprised his role as [[Kraglin Obfonteri (Earth-199999)|Kraglin]].<ref name="Guardians of the Galaxy"/>{{cite|ref=true|url= https://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-9208951/Chris-Hemsworth-Chris-Pratt-film-Thor-Sydney.html|title= Hollywood star Chris Hemsworth transforms himself into Thor as he shoots scenes with co-star Chris Pratt on the Love and Thunder set in Sydney|last= Taylor|first= Caleb|date= 01 February 2021|accessdate= 02 February 2021}} {{WP|Russell Crowe}} appeared as [[Zeus Panhellenios (Earth-199999)|Zeus]];{{cite|ref=true |url= https://deadline.com/2021/03/thor-love-and-thunder-russell-crowe-1234723853/|title= ‘Thor: Love And Thunder’: Russell Crowe Lands Role In Sequel|work= Deadline|last= Kroll|first= Justin|date= March 29, 2021|accessdate= March 30, 2021}}{{cite|ref=true|url= https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/joy-breakfast-with-the-murphys/id1525632251?i=1000517705859|title= Russell Crowe shares some awesome moments with The Murphys!|author= JOY Breakfast with The Murphys|date= April 22, 2021|accessdate= April 23, 2021}} and Akosia Sabet was cast as the Wakandan and [[Ennead|Egyptian goddess]] [[Bast (Earth-199999)|Bast]], marking her first direct appearance in the MCU.{{cite|ref=true |url=https://comicbook.com/marvel/news/thor-love-thunder-spoilers-bast-black-panther-god-confirmed-new-photo/|title=New Thor: Love and Thunder Photo Confirms Major Black Panther 2 Connection|work=Comicbook.com|last=Barnhardt|first=Adam|date=May 16, 2022|accessdate=May 22, 2022}}{{cite|ref=true|url=https://thedirect.com/article/black-panther-thor-4-character-photo|title=Black Panther Character Spotted In New Thor 4 Photo|work=The Direct|last=Chanliau|first=Pierre|date=May 17, 2022|accessdate=May 22, 2022}} Additionally, {{WP|Brett Goldstein}} appears as [[Hercules Panhellenios (Earth-199999)|Hercules]] in the mid-credits scene.

| Notes                   = * ''Thor: Love and Thunder'' was originally supposed to open on November 5, 2021, but was later moved to February 18, 2022 and then to February 11 due to the {{WP|COVID-19 pandemic}}.{{cite|ref=true|url= https://variety.com/2020/film/box-office/disney-mulan-black-widow-release-dates-coronavirus-1203550173/|title= ‘Black Widow,’ ‘Eternals,’ ‘Indiana Jones 5’ and More Disney Films Get New Release Dates|work= Variety|last= Rubin|first= Rebecca|date= April 3, 2020|accessdate= April 3, 2020}}{{cite|ref=true|refname=Deadline|url=https://deadline.com/2020/04/doctor-strange-2-heads-to-2022-thor-love-and-thunder-moves-up-a-week-1202917542/|title='Spider-Man: Homecoming' Sequel Pushes 'Doctor Strange 2' To 2022 As Disney & Sony Team On Release Date Changes|last=D'Alessandro|first=Anthony|date=April 24, 2020|accessdate=April 24, 2020}} Along with Bale's casting confirmation, Marvel also announced that the film would be pushed back once again to May 6, 2022.{{cite|ref=true|url=https://twitter.com/MarvelStudios/status/1337200046849159170|title=Academy Award-winning actor Christian Bale will join the cast of Thor: Love and Thunder as the villain Gorr the God Butcher. In theaters May 6, 2022.|author=Marvel Studios|work=Twitter|date=10 December 2020|accessdate=11 December 2020}} The release date was later taken by {{sl|Doctor Strange in the Multiverse of Madness}}, pushing this film back to July 8, 2022, taking the release date of {{ml|Black Panther: Wakanda Forever}}.{{cite|ref=true|url= https://variety.com/2021/film/news/disney-delays-doctor-strange-thor-black-panther-1235091673/|title= Disney Delays ‘Doctor Strange 2,’ ‘Thor 4,’ ‘Black Panther’ Sequel and ‘Indiana Jones 5’|work= Variety|last= Rubin|first= Rebecca|date= October 18, 2021|accessdate= October 18, 2021}}
* Principal photography for this film started on January 26, 2021,{{cite|ref=true|url= https://www.digitalspy.com/movies/a35316864/chris-hemsworth-thor-love-and-thunder-photo/|title= Chris Hemsworth confirms Thor: Love and Thunder has started filming with behind-the-scenes photos|work= Digital Spy|last= McCreesh|first= Louise|date= January 26, 2021|accessdate= January 27, 2021}} and wrapped on June 1{{cite|ref=true|url=https://www.marvel.com/articles/movies/thor-love-and-thunder-wraps-filming|title='Thor: Love and Thunder' Wraps Filming|last=Dinh|first=Christine|work=Marvel.com|date=June 1, 2021|accessdate=June 2, 2021}}

| Trivia                  = * The armor Thor wears during the attack on New Asgard resembles the armor he wore to hold himself together after Hela put a curse on him.
